snippet.title: Super Mario Moonlight - F3 Trailer
snippet.description: Super Mario Moonlight is a mod for Super Mario 3D World + Bowser's Fury coming April 2025. As of now, the mod is almost finished and almost ready for release! You can join my discord server for more information on the mod! :) https://discord.gg/j8cwURMT4V
